### For Developers

```shell
# Activate the virtual environment to start using it
. .venv/bin/activate # or .venv/bin/activate.fish

# Run the command.
$ momtag --dry-run --verbose ~/Music

# Or, if you want to debug the application, use the supplied main.py script.
$ python main.py
```


